text: Thanks for adding the main page scrolling capability! But it looks like there is still a UI bug with the Plan and Build sidebars - here you can see how the contents of the sidebar goes past the height of the screen and breaks scrolling, also causing an ugly blank area beneath the contents on the left. Instead, the sidebar should only be as tall as the screen/view, and scroll if the contents are longer than that.
taskTitles: Fix Plan and Build sidebar overflow causing broken scrolling and blank area below content
